{
  "title": "Magical Low-Cal Mexican Chicken Mole Poblano",
  "description": "A funky, shaggy, date-night Mexican dish featuring sesame seed burger buns and candy, with a low-calorie twist on traditional Oaxacan mole poblano.",
  "cuisine": "Mexican",
